23
00:01:10,710 --> 00:01:13,440
The downside is that you've to make sure that whatever you put in

24
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:14,995
continues to play nice with edX.

25
00:01:14,995 --> 00:01:18,120
You're putting in custom JavaScript, which means it could break at any time

26
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,230
when they update.

27
00:01:19,230 --> 00:01:21,810
And so every time, you've got to kind of check.

28
00:01:21,810 --> 00:01:24,750
Every couple weeks, make sure it's still there.

29
00:01:24,750 --> 00:01:27,660
And also a lot of students who take edX courses

30
00:01:27,660 --> 00:01:29,340
have taken previous edX courses.

31
00:01:29,340 --> 00:01:33,750
So while edX's default navigation isn't great,

32
00:01:33,750 --> 00:01:36,900
