33
00:01:36,900 --> 00:01:39,780
you want to make sure that the alternative navigation you put in

34
00:01:39,780 --> 00:01:40,830
isn't confusing them.

35
00:01:40,830 --> 00:01:43,815
I like to think of it more as supplemental navigation, that what

36
00:01:43,815 --> 00:01:45,690
you're putting in isn't meant to replace edX,

37
00:01:45,690 --> 00:01:48,760
but it is meant to provide an enhancement on what's already there.

38
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:51,485
So be sure you're clear about what you're showing

39
00:01:51,485 --> 00:01:52,860
with your alternative navigation.

40
00:01:52,860 --> 00:01:55,820
